race.comment: MISLUDI (11) will appreciate the drop in grade and only needs to hold her form to break a long run of outs. Will relish the anticipated tempo and should blend into the race nicely from her middle draw. Watch for her launching on them. FASHION DOG (7) has worked home well late in his last two, after kicking off the prep in perfect order. Peak fitness now and keeps Toeroek. Big chance. TRIPOD TERROR (5) has mixed his form since resuming but gets his chance to put it altogether on the quick back-up. Watch for him bursting through when they quicken. WALLY WEST (3) broke a long run of outs when resuming this campaign but has failed to go on with it against tougher opposition in his last two. Is much better placed back in this grade and looks a genuine threat.
